Package: spreadview
Title: Quickly export survey results into MS Excel spreadsheet
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Aleš", "Vomáčka", , "ales@vomacka.io", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Export data (usually) from opinion survey into a nicely readable MS Excel spreadsheet.
    Based on data.table and openxlsx2. Supports categorical variables only for now.
